<div class="container-fluid homePost">
  <h1>Welcome!</h1>
  <h5>Hey Guys, Welcome to Dear Diary. This is place where you can pour your heart out. You can read, you can write, you can learn, you can enjoy :). So for writing your own dear diary moment click on the 'Compose' at the top right corner. Enjoy!
